title: Hands Never Sleep & joebryant. - From Rivers To Arches Split
description:
Hey guys, this is the new Hands Never Sleep split EP with joebryant. It's a collection of acoustic songs (and a few covers) we recorded within a few weeks to showcase our different styles in a similar setting. The first three songs are HNS tracks, including an Anthony Green cover. The second half of the EP includes a few originals by joebryant. and a Bad Books cover. Check it out, check out my other torrents (for more original music), and if you like what you hear, check out the links below.
